{"tid":545179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幾時到支那大媽]大聲叫賣影響居民　元朗「招仔記」被罰3000元","createTime":"2018-01-30T09:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T06:17:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5fb1a0dd00c07f38e6c7f8dae619038613af47","tid":545179,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180130/s00001/1517300530126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180130%2Fs00001%2F1517300530126&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=ad7bb169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180130%2Fs00001%2F1517300530126&h=b60d8f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180130/s00001/1517300530126</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗合財街「招仔記」蔬菜店，因營業時持續大聲播放叫賣錄音，造成噪音煩擾。粉嶺裁判法院裁定違反《噪音管制條例》，罰款3000元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n環保署表示，去年多次接獲市民投訴，投訴合財街有商戶在營業時發出叫賣噪音，影響附近居民。署方去年9月聯同警方巡查，發現「招仔記」透過店舖門前揚聲器，不斷大聲播放宣傳錄音，遂按《噪音管制條例》起訴店方。<br />\n<br />\n環保署提醒零售店舖與商販負責人，為招徠顧客而播放宣傳錄音，聲量只能限於店舖內，不可對店外其他人造成煩擾。<br />\n<br />\n根據《噪音管制條例》，在店舖範圍推廣宣傳時對其他人士造成噪音煩擾，即屬違法，最高可罰款1萬元。"},{"pid":"0667dda8f1e31d1620b4cfc70d5090faab4c907f","tid":545179,"uid":142544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"大圍有條街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ff884914a48a4ebec376ccc1c822f80a5fefc4","tid":545179,"uid":121200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0667dda8f1e31d1620b4cfc70d5090faab4c907f","tid":545179,"uid":142544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"大圍有條街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"深水埗都係一樣，仲要某 d 錄音既人講野有鄉音，d 聲又拆，嘈撚到